                    <span>This is a good book and really made me want to start drawing and writing again. It is just plain fun</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Comfort Food for your Creative Soul!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>10</span>
