                    </div>
                    <span>This little book joins me each morning with tea and toast. It is brimming with great ideas, encouragement and wisdom that gets my creative engine turning over at the beginnning of each day. More human and optimistic than The Artist's Way, Living out Loud is a workbook, a playspace,a bible and a cheerleader that gets me excited to make more things in every part of my life. A rare gift.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">so much light in such a little book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
